<br>
CoH has a sort of mind wipe component as well as teleporting the target of the spell to the caster (mage). It used to be that the spell would clear aggro on the target (usually a puller) without a minimum distance. Verant deemed that the spell such as this is too powerful and open to exploit so they nerfed the spell and require a minimum range of 100 feet from caster to target before the memwipe (remove aggro) component would work. CoH was once considered by Verant to be too powerful and was supposed to be removed from the game but they decided to just nerf it. <p><p><a
